{"tid":1726573,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"藍絲拆路障唔好理佢地，重起","createTime":"2019-11-16T08:23:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T14:21:13.000Z","uid":94771,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"124ac95f7019704285af8635ba247e05c8ffa24a","tid":1726573,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:23:14.000Z","msg":"第一，注意好多人叫手足使用武力，<strong>如果對方只係拆路障你就去用武力打人會令文宣好難做</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n第二，藍絲人數好多，如果打大家難免好容易受傷，手足唔應該浪費自己力量去搞藍絲<br />\n<br />\n第三，跌佐入政府想我地民打民的圈套。藍絲只係政府Condom中的Condom，<strong>對面死傷幾多政府根本唔介意，政府完全無損傷。</strong><br />\n<br />\n第四，有人話用火魔，火魔其實極限都係對黑狗，因為大家武力不對等，所以用都係大條道理，但對空手的藍絲用火魔就已經完全過佐火，<strong>政府最想就係見到<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍絲</span>比火魔燒死。</strong>"},{"pid":"3f570ec86e116286b66ac29f688e9719db7f541b","tid":1726573,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:23:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01f3673a6e3eda1d4c7f3710b4feb1985bc8c210","tid":1726573,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:26:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c916f9febd83c99be1433e06c79ebcee22d9b528","tid":1726573,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:42:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20b107fd524dcdd5d304042e9ba11864e9baef12","tid":1726573,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:08:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"452c77c6e4938c64819993f6c6caa071ba42e462","tid":1726573,"uid":25771,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:10:02.000Z","msg":"驚就驚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad7e8dbdfed5c77e890bee890353fed1a74048bb","tid":1726573,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:10:50.000Z","msg":"****眾籌****<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，仲係要借個位&amp;幫你推推POST<br />\n<br />\n鍾庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721, 831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先64%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持)<br />\n<br />\n第五期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1</a> <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXjk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=3b3a1db8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2F&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXjk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=752ec82d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n(對唔住，咁危難時刻下我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做，行得通就全力去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"823ff45f19f63edb79566aa50a7d4fc1554b6d34","tid":1726573,"uid":35125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"452c77c6e4938c64819993f6c6caa071ba42e462","tid":1726573,"uid":25771,"like":0,"disl